<br>
FD was orginally not a skill to be used as it is in everquests orginal &quot;vision&quot;.  Varent has never changed it and have started to develop EQ based on it instead.  Since Velious an enchanter is nothing but a buff whore, and monks don't need enchanters period.  The moon is worst then velious.<br>
<br>
The ratio's of equipment available for a monk is sickening.<br>
<br>
Epic Haste 40 percent, Average haste item 36 percent,  that's 76 percent right there.  Why is monk epic haste a song that stacks with Item haste?  Why do Monks and rogues have epic Haste and a Warrior is suppose to be the taunt factor, but have no epic haste, not to mention sucky delay.<br>
<br>
