<br>
Imo the monk class has destroyed 2 other classes in game.  That being the enchanter and Mage class.  You can replace any Enc on a high end raid with a Shaman.  The mage spell Coth should of been the only form of splitting mobs imo, having it at level 55 was very appropiate.<br>
<br>
Who the hell really wants to raid in Velious or on the moon as a Enc?  Oh Kei dropped? Wait let me follow that up with Visions of grandeur for the tanks... /afk 44 mins.<br>
<br>
This topic is referring to how comparable a monk is for tanking.  Ya they ain't replacing warriors yet, but I think they will next expansion, they are getting a form of Kei also to give to the 1 cleric they group with.<br>
<br>
